@startuml
title BP-24 - Payment Initiation through Payment Gateway

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Parent Guardian|
start
:Select digital payment method;
:Confirm payment order;

|Platform|
:Validate order status is PENDING;
:Validate payment method is allowed;
:Prepare payment gateway request;

|Payment Gateway|
:Create payment instruction;
if (Gateway accepts request?) then (Yes)
  :Return QRIS, virtual account or redirect data;
else (No)
  :Return gateway error;
  stop
endif

|Platform|
:Save reference number and payment instruction;

|Parent Guardian|
:Complete payment outside or inside gateway channel;
stop

note right
Current MVP stores payment method and reference number.
Actual external gateway integration is future scope.
end note
@enduml
